THE SEGMENTS. SEGMENT INFORMATION APPEARING IN NOTE 22  SEGMENT INFORMATION AND GEOGRAPHIC DATA OF THE NOTES TO FINANCIAL STATEMENTS (PART II, ITEM 8) IS PRESENTED ON A BASIS CONSISTENT WITH OUR CURRENT INTERNAL MANAGEMENT REPORTING, IN

