PRODUCTS. THIS GROWTH REFLECTS BROAD ADOPTION OF THE WINDOWS PLATFORM AND APPLICATIONS WITH THE RELEASES OF WINDOWS SERVER 2008 AND VISUAL STUDIO 2008 DURING FISCAL YEAR 2008. CONSULTING AND PREMIER PRODUCT SUPPORT SERVICES REVENUE INCREASED $593

