CONTINUED MIGRATION OF SUBSCRIBERS TO BROADBAND OR OTHER COMPETITIVELY-PRICED SERVICE PROVIDERS. FOREIGN CURRENCY EXCHANGE RATES ACCOUNTED FOR A $28 MILLION OR ONE PERCENTAGE POINT DECREASE IN REVENUE.

