BY OUR BOARD OF DIRECTORS DURING THE FIRST QUARTER OF FISCAL YEAR 2009. AS OF JUNE 30, 2009, APPROXIMATELY $34.5 BILLION REMAINED OF THE $40.0 BILLION APPROVED REPURCHASE AMOUNT. ALL REPURCHASES WERE MADE USING CASH RESOURCES. THE REPURCHASE

